  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was so intrigued, and I also felt so overburdened that I didn't sleep the first two nights of the trial, and I practically fell asleep on the third night of the-- or the third day of the trial.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Part of the time.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for instance, I was assigned to California for about [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] two months.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I became involved out there in a very ticklish situation, which involved the associated farmers who had committed assaults on some picketers outside the JG Boswell Company, which was one of the largest producers of economic wares in products in California at that time.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] went down to hold some meetings, and the associated farmers stationed cars across from my little hotel out at this small town where this, some of this violence had taken part.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the associated farmers are trying to intimidate any witnesses from coming in the hotel.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the minister, who was the, actually the local organizer of these workers, came in and said, you aren't going to have any more witnesses, because those two cars are scaring them away.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I hired a newspaper boy to go over and find the names out, if he could find the names of a couple of them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He did, and I phoned them into Los Angeles.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, I'm going over there, and I just want you to know the number of these two cars that are intimidating me and all that, and I'm going over to open the car doors.",
      "word_count": 35
    }
  ],
